# UI components

## shadcn / Tailwind

- Primitives live in `components/ui/` (Button, Input, ScrollArea, etc.)
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes
- Design tokens: CSS variables in `app/globals.css` (`bg-background`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, etc.)
- Icons: `lucide-react`
- New shadcn components: follow `components.json` aliases (`@/components/ui`)

## Client vs server

| File | Directive | Why |
|------|-----------|-----|
| `app/page.tsx` | `'use client'` | `useChat`, form state, refs |
| `app/login/page.tsx` | `'use client'` | `useActionState` |
| `components/NavBar.tsx` | `'use client'` | `usePathname`, logout form |
| `app/layout.tsx` | Server | metadata, font, shell |

Hide chrome on login: `NavBar` returns `null` when `pathname === '/login'`.

## Patterns

- External nav links: `<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">`
- Server actions in forms: `<form action={logoutAction}>` or `formAction` from `useActionState`
- Loading: `Loader2` + `animate-spin`; disabled states on inputs/buttons during pending/streaming
- Layout: `h-dvh`, `max-w-2xl`, sticky nav with `backdrop-blur`

## Accessibility

- Meaningful labels/placeholders on login and chat input
- `autoComplete="off"` on token field
